summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 7W, page 46 of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Replat of Oneida Gardens Addition, all of Blocks 37, 38, 39, 40, 41, 42, 43, 44, 53, 54, 55, 56, 57, 58, 59, 60, 69, 72, as Single Family Residence High Density (RS 5000) Zone.
